      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is a total gem! This beauty has been meticulously pampered and is in truly flawless condition\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here; it's been loved and garage-kept since day one. I'm so excited for someone else to get behind the wheel of such a perfect ride. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 44500.0,
