    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable 1995 Mazda RX-7, a masterclass in lightweight engineering. The 13B-REW rotary powerplant features a flawlessly functioning sequential twin-turbocharger system, delivering linear boost across the rev range. This chassis remains rigid with zero oxidation, retaining its original double-wishbone geometry and factory-spec Torsen LSD. All vacuum lines have been meticulously maintained to prevent boost leaks, ensuring the apex seals maintain optimal compression. The five-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement with a precise throw, paired with a pristine interior that reflects its collector-grade status. This is a turn-key, investment-quality FD for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
